snippet.title: Is Johnny Depp the father of Amber Heard's new born baby? | Flixet
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to discuss the amber heard's newborn baby.

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_________________________________________________

Amber Heard announced the birth of her daughter, Oonagh Paige Herd, in an Instagram post. In the long and candid text, the actress told her subscribers that she decided to have a child on her own terms four years ago and wanted to normalize women with children without being married.
